Package: chorechill-ctl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.8), python3-tk, libcjson1
Recommends: python3-customtkinter
Description: Modular fan control daemon for Linux laptops
 A low-level fan control daemon that communicates directly with the laptop
 Embedded Controller (EC) via /sys/kernel/debug/ec/ec0/io.
 .
 Uses a plugin-based architecture to support different motherboard families.
 Includes a Python GUI frontend and a hardware detection utility.
